Source: postgresbson
Section: database
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Ruohang Feng <rh@vonng.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), postgresql-all (>= 217~), pkgconf, libbson-dev
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no
Homepage: https://github.com/buzzm/postgresbson

Package: postgresql-PGVERSION-pgbson
Architecture: any
Provides: postgresql-pgbson
Depends: ${postgresql:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: BSON data type and accessor functions for PostgreSQL
  postgresbson provides the pgbson PostgreSQL extension, which adds a BSON data
  type together with accessor, comparison, and conversion functions.
